---------Docker Volume ----------

1 run container and show a html file 
	-first create a folder named website
	-create a index.html file 
	-open terminal on index.html directory and 
	-use this command
	
	sudo docker run --name website -v $(pwd):/usr/share/nginx/html:ro -d -p 3000:80 nginx
	
	now run on port 3000
	
2 enter into the container
	sudo docker exec -it website bash


3  
